{"tid":1082820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"夠膽坐隔籬？女怪客抬頭狂咳　疑吐痰再腳踩","createTime":"2019-03-29T08:00:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T08:07:50.000Z","uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a51a78179c4a09bfccfadb7a1bfd181667ec4a74","tid":1082820,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T08:00:29.000Z","msg":"夠膽坐隔籬？女怪客抬頭狂咳 疑吐痰再腳踩<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2V2tUF5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2V2tUF5&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HexpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=9a6c0d66\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2V2tUF5</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190329/photo/bkn-20190329141617395-0329_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190329155055\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190329%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190329141617395-0329_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190329155055&h=378ff42f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天氣咁熱，怕唔怕溶妝？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搭車顧自己，都要顧人哋。近日港鐵車廂內有女子疑似隨地吐痰，咳嗽時亦沒掩住口鼻，網民紛紛怒斥其罔顧他人！<br />\n<br />\n有目擊者於周五（29日）在Facebook群組「將軍澳」發貼指，早上約11時在港鐵將軍澳綫遇見一名自私女子：「我本身坐佢側邊個位，佢一坐落嚟係咁咳咳咳，我立即起身企咗去另一邊。啱啱感冒先好番，驚畀佢傳染」。<br />\n<br />\n發貼者指，該女乘客口中唸唸有詞，疑似講粗口罵人，又吐口水。據片段可見，該濃妝艷抹的女子蹺着雙腳就座，腳底附近有水漬，旁邊的乘客不時察看，打量女子。其後，她抬頭咳嗽時沒有掩嘴，一旁乘客見狀馬上用手遮住口鼻。<br />\n<br />\n不少網友大呼恐怖：「頭先見過佢呀！佢個妝好得人驚！黑色眼影好似貼上去咁」、「搵地鐵職員做佢囉，不可助長此風」，有人揶揄：「最佩服佢身邊啲人，見佢自言自語，又咳都唔彈開，死都要黐住張櫈，為咗坐都要接受咳嗽細菌，勁啊」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190329/photo/bkn-20190329141617395-0329_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190329155055\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190329%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190329141617395-0329_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190329155055&h=6f915d07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女子腳旁有數處水漬。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190329/photo/bkn-20190329141617395-0329_00822_001_03p.jpg?20190329155055\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190329%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190329141617395-0329_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20190329155055&h=eeb43820&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一旁乘客見女子咳嗽即掩住口鼻。（互聯網）"},{"pid":"a31915fbcb6e968fe213eb454315adec99be6148","tid":1082820,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T08:05:40.000Z","msg":"哇面粉上妝呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11507f76d36bf564093da9e1fd5d8354d6753259","tid":1082820,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T08:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n地錢間唔時都遇到痴線佬"}]}